data.description: Are you looking for a character-filled home with multiple garage stalls & expansive exterior yard space?  Look no further than this gem in Lynd, MN.  Only a short drive into Marshall, MN - take the opportunity to own all this space at a pretty price point.  Important points on this property: 2017 roof/vinyl siding & dishwasher * LR large window & UL Bath window replaced * 2020 Water Heater. Seller has been working on painting, updating flooring, fixing the exterior deck space, so that you can move in and call it YOURS - get on the books today with your preferred Realtor!
